<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=5.0, user-scalable=yes, viewport-fit=cover" />
  <title>Nadia · Art Director & Digital Strategist</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      background-color: #fffbf5;
      font-family: "Manrope", sans-serif;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: #493f55;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      width: 100%;
    }

    /* —— 4-COLUMN MASTER GRID (Desktop) —— */
    .master-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      column-gap: 20px;
      padding: 0 2vw;
      margin: 0 auto;
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
    }

    /* Typography */
    h1 {
      font-family: "Manrope", sans-serif;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 82px;
      line-height: 1.05;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #493f55;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      margin-top: 60px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-family: "Manrope", sans-serif;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 50px;
      line-height: 1.1;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #493f55;
    }

    h3 {
      font-family: "Manrope", sans-serif;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 30px;
      line-height: 1.2;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #493f55;
    }

    h4 {
      font-family: "Manrope", sans-serif;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 30px;
      line-height: 1.25;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #6d3aff;
    }

    p {
      font-family: "Manrope", sans-serif;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #493f55;
    }

    button,
    .button {
      background-color: #ff914d;
      border: none;
      color: #fffbf5;
      font-family: "Manrope", sans-serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 13px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.4px;
      transition: background 0.25s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
      text-decoration: none;
      white-space: nowrap;
      line-height: 1;
      min-height: 48px;
      -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
      touch-action: manipulation;
    }

    button:hover,
    .button:hover {
      background-color: #e07b3c;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    button:active,
    .button:active {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    .arrow-icon-left {
      display: inline-block;
      transform: rotate(180deg);
      width: 16px;
      height: 16px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    /* Photo circle */
    .photo-circle {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #f3ede5;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      overflow: hidden;
      background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, #e5d9cc 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 16px 16px;
      color: #b7aa9a;
      font-size: 13px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .photo-circle img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
    }

    /* Cards */
    .cards-container {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .card {
      flex: 1;
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 20px 16px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .card h4 {
      font-size: 30px;
      color: #6d3aff;
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Utility spacing */
    .spacer-80 {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      height: 80px;
    }

    .spacer-40 {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      height: 40px;
    }

    /* Grid placement classes */
    .grid-full {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }
    .grid-1 {
      grid-column: 1 / 2;
    }
    .grid-2 {
      grid-column: 2 / 3;
    }
    .grid-3 {
      grid-column: 3 / 4;
    }
    .grid-4 {
      grid-column: 4 / 5;
    }
    .grid-1-2 {
      grid-column: 1 / 3;
    }
    .grid-2-4 {
      grid-column: 2 / 5;
    }
    .grid-3-4 {
      grid-column: 3 / 5;
    }
    .grid-2-3 {
      grid-column: 2 / 4;
    }

    /* Subgrid container for mission/values */
    .subgrid-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: subgrid;
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      gap: 0;
    }

    .mission-col {
      grid-column: 1 / 2;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .values-col {
      grid-column: 3 / 5;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .values-inner-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 20px 20px;
    }

    .value-block {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    /* Button alignment inside mission column */
    .mission-col .button-wrapper {
      margin-top: auto;
    }

    /* ======================================== */
    /*   TABLET: 768px – 1024px (8 columns)     */
    /* ======================================== */
    @media screen and (max-width: 1024px) {
      .master-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(8, 1fr);
        column-gap: 16px;
        padding: 0 3vw;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 52px;
        letter-spacing: -0.3px;
        margin-top: 48px;
      }
      h2 {
        font-size: 36px;
        line-height: 1.1;
      }
      h3 {
        font-size: 24px;
        line-height: 1.25;
      }
      h4 {
        font-size: 22px;
        line-height: 1.25;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 1.65;
      }
      button,
      .button {
        font-size: 12px;
        padding: 13px 24px;
        border-radius: 18px;
      }
      .card {
        padding: 16px 14px;
        gap: 16px;
        border-radius: 20px;
      }
      .card h4 {
        font-size: 20px;
      }
      .card p {
        font-size: 12px;
      }

      .spacer-80,
      .spacer-40 {
        grid-column: 1 / -1 !important;
      }

      /* Tablet grid overrides */
      h1.grid-full {
        grid-column: 1 / -1 !important;
      }
      .grid-1 {
        grid-column: 1 / 3;
      }
      .grid-2 {
        grid-column: 3 / 5;
      }
      .grid-3 {
        grid-column: 5 / 7;
      }
      .grid-4 {
        grid-column: 7 / 9;
      }
      .grid-1-2 {
        grid-column: 1 / 5;
      }
      .grid-2-4 {
        grid-column: 3 / 9;
      }
      .grid-3-4 {
        grid-column: 5 / 9;
      }
      .grid-2-3 {
        grid-column: 3 / 7;
      }

      .photo-circle {
        max-width: 200px;
      }

      .subgrid-row {
        grid-template-columns: subgrid;
      }
      .mission-col {
        grid-column: 1 / 3;
      }
      .values-col {
        grid-column: 5 / 9;
      }

      .values-inner-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 16px;
      }
    }

    /* ======================================== */
    /*   MOBILE: до 767px — ВСЁ В КОЛОНКУ      */
    /* ======================================== */
    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
      .master-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        column-gap: 0;
        padding: 0 24px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0;
      }

      .grid-full,
      .grid-1,
      .grid-2,
      .grid-3,
      .grid-4,
      .grid-1-2,
      .grid-2-4,
      .grid-3-4,
      .grid-2-3,
      .spacer-80,
      .spacer-40,
      h1,
      h2,
      h3,
      h4 {
        grid-column: auto !important;
        width: 100% !important;
        max-width: 100% !important;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 42px;
        line-height: 1.1;
        margin-top: 48px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        text-align: left;
      }
      h2 {
        font-size: 32px;
        line-height: 1.15;
        text-align: left;
        margin: 0;
      }
      h2 br {
        display: none;
      }
      h3 {
        font-size: 22px;
        line-height: 1.25;
        text-align: left;
        margin: 0;
      }
      h4 {
        font-size: 20px;
        line-height: 1.3;
        text-align: left;
        margin: 0 0 32px 0;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.65;
      }

      .spacer-80 {
        height: 48px;
        width: 100%;
      }
      .spacer-40 {
        height: 32px;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .cards-container {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 16px;
        width: 100%;
      }
      .card {
        flex: none;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 20px 16px;
        gap: 14px;
        border-radius: 20px;
      }
      .card h4 {
        font-size: 22px;
      }
      .card p {
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .photo-circle {
        max-width: 180px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .subgrid-row {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 40px;
      }
      .mission-col,
      .values-col {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .values-inner-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 24px;
      }

      button,
      .button {
        width: 100% !important;
        justify-content: center !important;
        border-radius: 25px;
        padding: 16px 24px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .button-wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        margin-top: 24px;
      }

      .master-grid > div:last-child {
        height: 64px;
      }
    }

    /* ======================================== */
    /*   SMALL MOBILE: < 380px                  */
    /* ======================================== */
    @media screen and (max-width: 380px) {
      .master-grid {
        padding: 0 20px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 36px;
        margin-top: 40px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      h2 {
        font-size: 28px;
      }
      h3 {
        font-size: 20px;
      }
      h4 {
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 13px;
      }

      .spacer-80 {
        height: 40px;
      }
      .spacer-40 {
        height: 24px;
      }

      .card {
        padding: 16px 14px;
      }
      .card h4 {
        font-size: 20px;
      }

      button,
      .button {
        padding: 14px 20px;
        font-size: 13px;
      }

      .photo-circle {
        max-width: 150px;
      }
    }

    /* ======================================== */
    /*   LARGE DESKTOP: > 1600px                */
    /* ======================================== */
    @media screen and (min-width: 1600px) {
      .master-grid {
        max-width: 1800px;
        padding: 0 5vw;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 96px;
      }
    }

    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      * {
        animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
        animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
        transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="master-grid">

    <!-- H1 -->
    <h1 class="grid-full">Hello, I'm Nadia</h1>

    <!-- Spacer 40px -->
    <div class="spacer-40"></div>

    <!-- Photo (column 1) -->
    <div class="grid-1">
      <div class="photo-circle">
        <!-- Replace with your image: <img src="nadia.jpg" alt="Nadia" /> -->
        photo
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- h4 + text (columns 2-4 and column 2) -->
    <h4 class="grid-2-4" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
      I am an Art Director, digital strategist, and creator of thoughtful, human-centered visual systems.
    </h4>

    <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top: 10px;">
      <p>
        Fluent in both languages — creative and commercial. Art direction, digital products, advertising, with a decade of international brand work and an aerospace engineering background. Open to brand campaigns, film, and digital products.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Spacer 80px -->
    <div class="spacer-80"></div>

    <!-- h2 what do i do (cols 1-2) -->
    <h2 class="grid-1-2">
      what do i do <br>for your project?
    </h2>

    <!-- Spacer 40px -->
    <div class="spacer-40"></div>

    <!-- First 3 cards (cols 2-4) -->
    <div class="grid-2-4">
      <div class="cards-container">
        <div class="card" style="background: #e0f9f3;">
          <h4>visual identity</h4>
          <p>That express a brand’s inner architecture, not just its surface aesthetics.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="background: #faeaf2;">
          <h4>websites & digital</h4>
          <p>Where clarity, emotion, and functionality support each other.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="background: #e0f9f3;">
          <h4>conceptual direction</h4>
          <p>For photoshoots, campaigns, and creative teams.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Spacer 20px -->
    <div style="grid-column: 1 / -1; height: 20px;"></div>

    <!-- Next 2 cards (cols 3-4) -->
    <div class="grid-3-4">
      <div class="cards-container">
        <div class="card" style="background: #fff4d4;">
          <h4>product communication</h4>
          <p>From positioning to narrative to the logic behind every touchpoint.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="background: #faeaf2; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px;">
          <h4>integrate technology</h4>
          <p>Ensuring tools (CRM, automation, bots, interfaces) serve the brand rather than complicate it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Spacer 80px -->
    <div class="spacer-80"></div>

    <!-- Mission & Values section using subgrid -->
    <div class="subgrid-row">
      <!-- Left: My Mission -->
      <div class="mission-col">
        <h2>My Mission</h2>
        <div style="height: 20px;"></div>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 12px;">
          To bring clarity, elegance, and emotional intelligence into the digital space.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 12px;">
          To build systems and visuals that feel alive, intuitive, and aligned with the true nature of the people and businesses behind them.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
          To show that technology can amplify human vision — not replace it.
        </p>
        <!-- Button aligned to bottom -->
        <div class="button-wrapper">
          <button class="button" style="width: auto;">
            <svg class="arrow-icon-left" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/>
            </svg>
            let's collaborate
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: My Values -->
      <div class="values-col">
        <h2 style="margin-bottom: 30px;">My Values</h2>
        <div class="values-inner-grid">
          <!-- Depth (left column) -->
          <div class="value-block">
            <h4>Depth</h4>
            <p>Everything meaningful grows from understanding. I study the client’s world until it becomes my own — their intentions, their audience, their patterns.</p>
          </div>
          <!-- empty right cell for alignment -->
          <div></div>

          <!-- Beauty (left) and Integrity (right) -->
          <div class="value-block">
            <h4>Beauty</h4>
            <p>Beauty is not decoration — it is communication. It creates trust, emotion, and memory.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-block">
            <h4>Integrity</h4>
            <p>Aesthetics matter, but honesty matters more. I design solutions that support the business long-term, not just decorate it.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Humanity (left) and Clarity (right) -->
          <div class="value-block">
            <h4>Humanity</h4>
            <p>No matter how advanced the tool, I design for humans first.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-block">
            <h4>Clarity</h4>
            <p>Confusion kills trust. I turn complexity into structure, chaos into direction, ideas into systems.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom breathing space -->
    <div style="grid-column: 1 / -1; height: 80px;"></div>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
